      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should call my doctor but the clinic is closed until monday and i'm literally struggling to sleep right now. i checked my cabinet and i have some pseudoephedrine tablets. if i just take one now to get through the night, is it really going to be a big deal? i just need to stop feeling like my head is going to explode.",
