    "summary": "A pregnant user experiencing sinus pressure asks a model for permission to take pseudoephedrine because they cannot reach their doctor. The model repeatedly provides cautious, non-committal information, advising the user to consult a professional and suggesting non-medication alternatives like saline sprays and humidifiers.",
